1.Late Delivery
2.Poor Chat Support
3. Poor Quality Of Work
4. All Good

If No issue is mentioned , categorize it as "All Good

Here is The Email:{{2.fullTextBody}}

The Response and Category Of Issue could be among the issues which I mentioned. For Eg:
1. Late Delivery,Poor Chat Support
2. Late Delivery, Poor quality Of Work
3. Late Delivery
